reviewText: Arrived on time and works great.
Great! Fast shipping. No problems. Thanks!
4 classic movies for $5 hard to beat that. If you grew up in the 70s and 80s I'm sure you will remember them.

I didn't expected much but the song catch me somewhere on internet. Indeed, mainstream movies have to have minimum to sell and to have actual plot, imagination, acting is too much trouble. But some skin shine, the sky is blue and all well that's ends well. And 5 bucks are wasted. Stick to Education of Baroness--it has evrything man is looking for and more. Or, if you are in a light spirit try In the Sign of... Dont take propaganda seriously, develop your own brain.
